title: Commercial property market value in the United Kingdom ( UK ) 2012 to 2016
summary: The timeline shows the global market value of the u.s. athletic and non-athletic footwear retail market from 2004 to 2011 . In 2014 , the global market value of the u.s. athletic and non-athletic footwear retail market was 24.6 percent . Between 2004 and 2017 , the global market share of the u.s. footwear retail market decreased by 3.0 percent .
